headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Pink and Green Camo Livery for Rank 100+ Players
content: To continue celebrating those with the discipline and focus required to ascent to truly great heights, players Rank 100 and above who play GTA Online this week will receive the rare Pink and Green Camo livery for the HVY Nightshark. Redeem and apply this elusive adornment in any Weaponized Vehicle Workshop (available within 72 hours of logging in after May 17th).
